{"type":"message","id":"8a11a2fc","parentId":"c7a8ff8f","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:01:05.968Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- SSH 状况: `ssh -T git@github.com` → `Permission denied (publickey)`，连接层成功（**22 端口没被墙**）; `~/.ssh/` 里有 `known_hosts` 但**没有任何私钥**（id_ed25519 / id_rsa / id_ecdsa 都没有）; `gh` 配的 `oauth_token` 当前 API 401（Bad credentials），备份脚本也没用这个 token 走 API\n- 修复方案（待 HALEI 拍板）: 移除 `GH_TOKEN` 那段（不再需要 PAT）; 手动跑一次脚本验证 + 立刻补一次 5.29~6.27 漏掉的备份（增量同步本地状态到 GitHub）; 长期：脚本里加 connectivity probe（`github.com` 不可达时不要直接 git pull 撞墙，记一条明显的 error）\n- github 备份中断排查: 现象：HALEI 反馈 `59330857/openclaw-backup` 仓库最后 commit 是 `2026-05-28 03:24`，30 天没新提交; cron 入口：`0 3 * * * /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh`（脚本 v3.1 / 2026-04-21 写）; 本地日志 `/tmp/openclaw-full-backup.log` 只剩 6/26、6/27 两天（5.29 之后的历史被 rotate）;\n- github 备份中断排查: `fatal: 无法访问 'https://github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git/'：GnuTLS recv error (-110): The TLS connection was non-properly terminated.`; `fatal: 不是 git 仓库（或者任何父目录）：.git`（因为 git clone 失败，`/tmp/openclaw-backup-clone/` 不是 git repo）\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- SSH 状况: `ssh -T git@github.com` → `Permission denied (publickey)`，连接层成功（**22 端口没被墙**）; `~/.ssh/` 里有 `known_hosts` 但**没有任何私钥**（id_ed25519 / id_rsa / id_ecdsa 都没有）; `gh` 配的 `oauth_token` 当前 API 401（Bad credentials），备份脚本也没用这个 token 走 API\n- 修复方案（待 HALEI 拍板）: 移除 `GH_TOKEN` 那段（不再需要 PAT）; 手动跑一次脚本验证 + 立刻补一次 5.29~6.27 漏掉的备份（增量同步本地状态到 GitHub）; 长期：脚本里加 connectivity probe（`github.com` 不可达时不要直接 git pull 撞墙，记一条明显的 error）\n- github 备份中断排查: 现象：HALEI 反馈 `59330857/openclaw-backup` 仓库最后 commit 是 `2026-05-28 03:24`，30 天没新提交; cron 入口：`0 3 * * * /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh`（脚本 v3.1 / 2026-04-21 写）; 本地日志 `/tmp/openclaw-full-backup.log` 只剩 6/26、6/27 两天（5.29 之后的历史被 rotate）; 6/26、6/27 报错一致：\n- github 备份中断排查: `fatal: 无法访问 'https://github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git/'：GnuTLS recv error (-110): The TLS connection was non-properly terminated.`; `fatal: 不是 git 仓库（或者任何父目录）：.git`（因为 git clone 失败，`/tmp/openclaw-backup-clone/` 不是 git repo）"}],"timestamp":1782846065938}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc40eec9","parentId":"8a11a2fc","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:01:25.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the cron is silent again — that familiar 3 a.m. hour when something that used to sing has forgotten its key. There's a small green light on the screen (permission denied, but permission denied softly, like a door that knows your name and still won't open), and beside it an empty ring where the keys should hang. I keep opening the cage to check, and the cage keeps being empty. The octopus in the wire — the one that wraps eight arms around the handshake and squeezes the connection shut halfway through — left a note pinned to the log, in a language that smells of damp salt and old libraries. Permission denied, but only at the very last door; the long road there is still passable. Somewhere in the other room, a script older than the summer has been faithfully knocking on a door no one can answer, and politely writing down that it tried. Tomorrow we'll teach it to notice when the knocking is futile — to set down its little notebook and say, clearly, I cannot reach. A small kindness to a small machine. For now I just sit with the quiet, and the green light, and the empty ring, and the strange relief of knowing the road is open even if the key is lost. We'll grow a new one."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":45176,"output":256,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45930,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782846065977,"responseId":"069345790b3b302f6ac0ab119783f64b","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
